---
title: Seared Pork Medallions with Brussels Sprouts, Roasted Potatoes and Tarragon-Cream Sauce
description: Served with shredded Brussels sprouts, creamy new potatoes, and a rich tarragon cream sauce, this six-ingredient dinner is worthy of any dinner party.
